---
title: "US19 — Workout reminders"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>NotificationsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpdateNotificationPrefs
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile (notification_prefs)
  A->>B: toggle "Daily reminder" on
  B->>C: setEnabled(daily_reminder, true)
  C->>E: update prefs map, persist
  E-->>C: saved
  C-->>B: toggle committed
  B-->>A: reminder fires at preferred time
  note over E: prefs via ProfileGateway → Supabase -<br/>scheduling rule-based via NotificationGateway (no AI)
